ef=\"https://github.com/kdeldycke/awesome-falsehood\">Falsehoods</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/kdeldycke/awesome-falsehood\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">16k</span></span></a> - A funny and educational list of why nothing in Software Development is ever easy. Think you can store a marriage in a DB?</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/minimaxir/big-list-of-naughty-strings\">Naughty Strings</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/minimaxir/big-list-of-naughty-strings\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">40.4k</span></span></a> - This is the famous list of Naughty Strings. If you're doing some field validation, look no further for inspiration.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/jagracey/Awesome-Unicode\">Unicode</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/jagracey/Awesome-Unicode\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">720</span></span></a> - A great resource for learning how unicode works and the issues it can cause.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"useful-references\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#useful-references\" aria-label=\"useful references permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Useful References</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\">The Original</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/sindresorhus/awesome\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">164.9k</span></span></a> - The awesome list of awesome lists.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/karlhorky/learn-to-program\">Learn to Code</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/karlhorky/learn-to-program\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.4k</span></span></a> - Learning to code, for those looking to make the move to automation</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/paragonie/awesome-appsec\">Application Security</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/paragonie/awesome-appsec\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">4.6k</span></span></a> - Incredibly extensive, but you'll find something to fit the bill.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/christian-bromann/awesome-selenium\">Selenium</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/christian-bromann/awesome-selenium\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">719</span></span></a> - Better than searching Google if you know what you want.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/sbilly/awesome-security\">Security</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/sbilly/awesome-security\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">7k</span></span></a> - This is mostly focused on Infrastructure, but if you're testing a series of systems, this is very useful.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ligurio/awesome-software-quality\">Awesome Software Quality</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/ligurio/awesome-software-quality\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1.9k</span></span></a> - A list of free software testing and verification resources.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/virajkulkarni14/awesome-cucumber\">Awesome Cucumber</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/virajkulkarni14/awesome-cucumber\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">25</span></span></a> - A (relatively-newer) curated list of awesome Cucumber and Gherkin-related resources.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/aliesbelik/awesome-jmeter\">Awesome JMeter</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/aliesbelik/awesome-jmeter\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">443</span></span></a> - A curated collection of resources around Apache JMeter.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/abhivaikar/howtheytest\">How They Test</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/abhivaikar/howtheytest\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">3.3k</span></span></a> - A curated collection of public resources from tech companies on how they test their software and build a quality culture</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"qa-and-testing-road-map\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#qa-and-testing-road-map\" aria-label=\"qa and testing road map permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>QA and Testing Road Map</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/fityanos/Quality-Assurance-Road-Map\">How to start QA and Testing career</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/fityanos/Quality-Assurance-Road-Map\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">587</span></span></a> - A wide and rich list of strategies, topics, and skills that you need to start a career in software testing and automation.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"others\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#others\" aria-label=\"others permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Others</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://play.spotify.com/user/sanchezni/playlist/5yzT0HrymwEeO8ckqgkPiW\">Testers Rage Playlist</a> - A collaborative playlist from testers for when the red mist descends.</li>\n<li><a href=\"http://testingconferences.org/\">Software Testing Conferences</a> - A list of software testing conferences and workshops.</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/TheJambo/ToDoInterviewTest\">Software Testing Interview Tool</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/TheJambo/ToDoInterviewTest\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">16</span></span></a> - A very buggy To Do List to facilitate face to face interviews.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"contributing\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#contributing\" aria-label=\"contributing permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Contributing</h2>\n<p>See the <em>Awesome Testing</em> <a href=\"https://github.com/TheJambo/awesome-testing/blob/master/CONTRIBUTING.md\">contribution guide</a> for details on how to contribute.</p>\n<h2 id=\"code-of-conduct\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#code-of-conduct\" aria-label=\"code of conduct permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 